per student per day
with effect from 01/04/2020
Primary
Rs. 4.97

The MDM SMS will be as follows -
1. SMS should be sent to 15544.
2. SMS will be through by a Registered Mobile Number only.
3. SMS should be sent from 10:10 am to 5:00 pm.
4. Mobile number can be changed through SMS Mode or Web Mode.
5. The official web portal “http://mdmhp.nic.in”
SMS format-
 MDM < Space> Nos. of meal served.
(Example: If MDM served 30 nos., then SMS format – MDM 30)
 If DMD is 0 then send SMS with proper Reason Code and Sub Reason
Code.

SMS Keywords:
MDM - Keyword for Daily Data.
MDM M - Keyword for Monthly Data.
MDM A - Keyword for Mobile verification and Activation.
MDM P - Modification of already registered mobile number.
MDM H - MDM help.
